                                                            <div class="row" style="padding: 5px 5px 5px 10px;margin-top: 10px;">
                                                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                                                    <ul style="text-align: justify;" >
                                                                        <li> <i class="fa fa-dot-circle-o"></i> &nbsp; The boring head is initially set on minimum mark on the scale.</li>
